参赛选手原有145个，但最终只有143名运动员出席。意大利人{{Link-en|达米亚诺·库内哥|Damiano Cunego}}还没有从[[2008年环法自行车赛|2008年环法大赛]]上受的伤中恢复过来，于是他的名额由[[温琴佐·尼巴利|温琴佐·尼巴利]]顶替。上届比赛银牌得主，葡萄牙人{{Link-en|赛尔吉奥·保林霍|Sérgio Paulinho}}声称身体尚无法进行比赛而没有参加。俄罗斯人{{Link-en|弗拉蒂米尔·古瑟夫|Vladimir Gusev}}因没有通过[[阿斯塔纳队|阿斯塔纳队]]的队内药物检测而被解雇，不能参加比赛，于是他的名额由{{Link-en|丹尼斯·门乔夫|Denis Menchov}}补上。在赛前训练中，瑞士队的{{Link-en|迈克尔·阿尔巴斯尼|Michael Albasini}}发生事故，[[锁骨|锁骨]]骨折，但此时瑞士已经没有时间寻找运动员顶替他参赛了<ref name=Withdrawals>{{citeweb |url=http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214511987.shtml |title=Four cyclists scratched from road race |publisher=The Official Website of the Beijing 2008 Olympic Games |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2008-08-09 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090428222455/http://en.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/headlines/cyclingroad/n214511987.shtml |archivedate=2009-04-28 }}</ref>。

== 赛前 ==
=== 污染问题 ===
奥运会开幕前，[[国际奥委会|国际奥委会]]希望降低比赛中空气污染的影响。而北京奥组委则准备在空气污染过高时改变某些比赛（如公路自行车赛）的赛程。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/olympics/cycling/7544928.stm|title=Bellis prepares for Beijing start|publisher=BBC|date=2008-08-06|accessdate=2008-08-09|language=En|archive-date=2017-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901120824/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/olympics/cycling/7544928.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>参加这类比赛的运动员所呼吸的氧气是一般人的20倍。因此，过高的空气污染会对比赛造成不利影响，对运动员的肺造成刺激或损伤，甚至加重呼吸系统疾病，例如[[哮喘|哮喘]]。<ref name=Pollution>{{citeweb|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7498198.stm|title=Beijing pollution: Facts and figures|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2008-08-08|accessdate=2008-08-09|language=En|archive-date=2017-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901115602/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/7498198.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據一個独立机构的数据，8月9日北京的空气污染高于[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]认定的安全级别。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/hq/2006/WHO_SDE_PHE_OEH_06.02_eng.pdf|title=Air quality guidelines – global update 2005 (pg. 12)|publisher=[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]|accessdate=2008-08-23|format=PDF|language=En|archive-date=2015-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150422003805/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/hq/2006/WHO_SDE_PHE_OEH_06.02_eng.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_pictures/7506925.stm|title=In pictures: Beijing pollution-watch|date=2008-08-06|accessdate=2008-08-09|publisher=BBC新闻|language=En|archive-date=2016-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623212451/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_pictures/7506925.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://online.wsj.com/public/resources/documents/info-flash07.html?project=BEIJINGSMOG0807&h=530&w=959&hasAd=1&settings=info-BEIJINGSMOG0807|title=Air Pollution in Beijing|publisher=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|accessdate=2008-08-23|language=En|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170945/http://online.wsj.com/public/resources/documents/info-flash07.html?project=BEIJINGSMOG0807&h=530&w=959&hasAd=1&settings=info-BEIJINGSMOG0807|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过，因为没有运动员提出异议，自行车赛事依旧按照原定计划举行。143名参赛运动员中，有53名中途退出了比赛，但这很正常（上一届比赛超过一半的运动员退出了比赛）。赛后，很多骑手批評恶劣的天气對表現有很大影响，尤其是[[摄氏|摄氏]]26度的高温和高達90%的相對濕度。这些条件比他们经常比赛的欧洲恶劣得多。相比之下，认为污染对比赛有较大的影响車手較少。<ref name=Sanchez>{{citeweb|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/olympics/cycling/7550885.stm|title=Sanchez clinches road race gold|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]体育|date=2008-08-09|accessdate=2008-08-09|language=En|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826194813/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/olympics/cycling/7550885.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是赛前的夺标热门，德國車手{{Link-en|斯特凡·舒马赫|Stefan Schumacher}}认为，嚴重的空气污染是导致他退赛的主因。<ref name=schumacher>{{citeweb|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/GCA-Olympics/idUSSP29740320080809|title=Spain's Sanchez wins men's road race|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|author=Deborah Charles|date=2008-08-09|accessdate=2008-08-14|language=En|archive-date=2009-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090703195057/http://www.reuters.com/article/GCA-Olympics/idUSSP29740320080809|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 赛前夺标热门 ===
赛前，西班牙代表队的所有骑手都是夺冠的热门<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.aol.com.au/news/story/Seven-gold-medals-on-opening-day/825971/index.html |title=Seven gold medals on opening day |publisher=[[美联社|美联社]] |date=2008-08-08 |accessdate=2008-08-12 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081229072416/http://www.aol.com.au/news/story/Seven-gold-medals-on-opening-day/825971/index.html |archivedate=2008-12-29 }}</ref>。他们中有两位[[三大赛事|三大赛事]]（[[环法|环法]]、[[环意大利自行车赛|环意大利]]和[[环西班牙自行车赛|环西班牙]]）的冠军：[[阿尔韦托·孔塔多尔|阿尔韦托·孔塔多尔]]及[[卡洛斯·萨斯特雷|卡洛斯·萨斯特雷]]，还有“乡下人”{{Link-en|西班牙国家公路自行车锦标赛|Spanish National Road Race Championships}}冠军{{Link-en|亚历杭德罗·巴尔韦德|Alejandro Valverde}}，以及在[[2007年环西班牙自行车赛|2007年环西赛]]三个赛段的冠军[[萨穆埃尔·桑切斯|萨穆埃尔·桑切斯]]。西班牙队还有2008年环法[[圆点衫|圆点衫]]得主，3次[[国际自行车联合会公路自行车世界杯|公路自行车世界杯]]冠军，西班牙队的领骑{{Link-en|奥斯卡·弗莱雷|Óscar Freire}}。其中，巴尔韦德被看作西班牙队的杀手锏<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://fannation.com/blogs/post/228636|title=Olympics: Cycling -- Men's Road Race|publisher=''体育画报''和[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2008-08-09|accessdate=2008-08-10|language=En|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108234901/http://fannation.com/blogs/post/228636|archive-date=2009-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=valverde2>{{citeweb |url=http://www.inquirer.net/specialfeatures/olympics/view.php?db=1&article=20080809-153652 |title=Sanchez of Spain wins Olympic road gold |publisher=[[法新社|法新社]] |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2008-08-10 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081002071334/http://www.inquirer.net/specialfeatures/olympics/view.php?db=1&article=20080809-153652 |archivedate=2008-10-02 }}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/olympics/2008/08/why_the_mens_cycling_road_race.html|title=Why 250km cycle route will favour Valverde|publisher=BBC体育|author=[[Simon_Brotherton|Simon Brotherton]]|quote=Alejandro Valverde is the name that keeps cropping up in previews ahead of the men's Olympic Road Race|date=2008-08-08|accessdate=2008-08-12|language=En|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307221530/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/olympics/2008/08/why_the_mens_cycling_road_race.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

被认为有机会获得奖牌的还有卫冕冠军，意大利人[[保罗·贝蒂尼|保罗·贝蒂尼]]<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.usacycling.org/news/user/story.php?id=3771|title=Olympic road race preview|publisher=[[美国自行车杂志|美国自行车杂志]]|date=2008-08-08|accessdate=2008-08-10|language=En|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081222093535/http://www.usacycling.org/news/user/story.php?id=3771|archive-date=2008-12-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=valverde2/>、德国的{{Link-en|斯特凡·舒马赫|Stefan Schumacher}}<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.moneyline.com/article/GCA-Olympics/idUSSP5468420080809 |title=Olympics – Cyclists wilt as Beijing competitors feel the heat |author=Francois Thomazeau |publisher=[[路透社|路透社]] |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2008-08-10 |language=En }}{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>，以及两届[[环法|环法]]亚军，澳大利亚人[[卡德尔·埃文斯|卡德尔·埃文斯]]。还有来自卢森堡队和德国队的队员们被看好<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.velonews.com/article/81419 |title=The 2008 Olympics - The Battle of Beijing |author=Fred Dreier |publisher=VeloNews |date=2008-08-07 |accessdate=2008-08-10 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080812043022/http://www.velonews.com/article/81419 |archivedate=2008-08-12 }}</ref>：德国队有舒马赫和很多参加过三大赛事的老将，如[[延斯·福格特|延斯·福格特]]；而卢森堡队拥有施莱克兄弟——[[安迪·施莱克|安迪]]和[[弗兰克·施莱克|弗兰克]]，以及[[金·基尔兴|金·基尔兴]]，这三名骑手都曾在2008年环法自行车赛上身着[[黄色领骑衫|黄色领骑衫]]出战<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.letour.fr/2008/TDF/LIVE/us/900/classement/index.html |title=Tour de France Roll of Honor Result after Stage 9 |publisher=[[环法自行车赛|环法自行车赛]] |date=2008-07-13 |accessdate=2008-08-18 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080818051803/http://www.letour.fr/2008/TDF/LIVE/us/900/classement/index.html |archivedate=2008-08-18 }}</ref><ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.letour.fr/2008/TDF/LIVE/us/1500/classement/index.html |title=Tour de France Roll of Honor Result after Stage 15 |publisher=环法自行车赛 |date=2008-07-20 |accessdate=2008-08-18 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080818040324/http://www.letour.fr/2008/TDF/LIVE/