很多为国家队领骑的车手都并没有寄希望于完成比赛<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.csc.com/mms/cycling/en/ne/na/articleDetail.jsp?id=14085 |title=Olympics: Cancellara Mines Bronze in Beijing |publisher=[[Computer_Sciences_Corporation|CSC]] |quote=(...) riders raced for the respective national squads in international competition. |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2008-08-10 |language=En |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081203144205/http://www.csc.com/cycling/news/8782-olympics_cancellara_mines_bronze_in_beijing |archivedate=2008-12-03 }}</ref>，他们确保了那些爬坡高手在坡道发力前可以有一个好的位置<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/results/2001/diary01/b_jones_thuringen.shtml|title=Ups and downs|author=Brice Jones|publisher=Cycling News|accessdate=2008-08-12|language=En|archive-date=2007-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017235142/http://www.cyclingnews.com/results/2001/diary01/b_jones_thuringen.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在他们之中，有很多运动员都需要为接下来的[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會男子公路自行車個人計時賽|个人计时赛]]节省体力。此外，如果一名运动员被超过一圈，那么他的比赛资格就会被取消<ref>{{cite web|url=http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/CHI/BCK/CR/39036.shtml|title=赛制与规则|publisher=2008年夏季奥运会官方网站|date=2008-08-08|accessdate=2009-04-24|language=zh-cn}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。
